    <refsection id="Description_mdaq_encoder">
        <title>Description</title>
        <para>
		
		This block reads MicroDAQ quadrature encoder. 'Init position' parameter allows to set initial value of quadrature encoder position register.
		
		</para>
		<para>This block can be used in host simulation mode and for code generation.</para>
    </refsection>
	
	<refsection id="InputOutput_mdaq_encoder">
        <title>Block Input/Output ports</title>
		<para>
		
		<member><para>input(1) - reset input - value different then 0 resets quadrature encode position register.(scalar)</para></member>
		<member><para>output(1) - quadrature encoder position(scalar)</para></member>
		<member><para>output(2) - direction - 0 - no motion, 1 - CW, 2 - CCW (scalar)</para></member>
		
		</para>
    
	</refsection>
